title: Covid19 Model using Ensemble Learning with 95% acc
description: In this kernal i'm going to create a predictive model for covid19 global-forecasting week 5 data which contains around 7 lakhs data for  training and we have to predict the target values for 3 lakhs test data In this model first i have did some analysis with the data with some graphs and also the the effect of corona in  India have been analysed seperately. Finally I created a ensemble learning model with almost 0.96 Rsquared score
